# === Telegram + Paresh Patches ===
# Format: +patch-name = include, -patch-name = exclude, # = comment

# 🔐 CORE PATCHES (Always enabled for functionality)
+ premium-features
+ bypass-integrity-check
+ open-restricted-channels
+ copy-save-forward-restricted
+ remove-sponsored-messages
+ anti-delete-messages
+ anti-disappearing-media

# ⚙️ OPTIONAL PATCHES (Disabled by default - uncomment to enable)
# 
# To ENABLE an optional patch, remove the '#' at the start of its line:
#
# + disable-auto-update
# + hide-typing-indicator
# + download-speed-boost

# ❌ EXPLICITLY EXCLUDE (prevent accidental inclusion)
- disable-auto-update
- hide-typing-indicator
- download-speed-boost
